Projects

Lumol – Ad-tech platform for conversational ads (Completed)

Lumol is an ad-tech platform that connects advertisers with LLM providers for conversational ad placements. I designed the platform to be minimalist and modern, with light, mid, and dark mode themes. The interface emphasizes clarity, usability, and seamless navigation, ensuring advertisers and AI providers can collaborate efficiently.

Role: Head Designer
Tools Used:
Figma (UI/UX design)
FigJam (flows and wireframes)
Adobe Suite (visual assets)
